{"tid":607664,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［請廣傳］賤男黃x灝借錢唔還走數（多圖）","createTime":"2018-03-27T13:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T14:26:09.000Z","uid":84918,"like":8,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c3f6624fce0c8d914dabab62368ac2eb995bd4cc","tid":607664,"uid":84918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T13:00:05.000Z","msg":"先黎一幅撚頭照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/222959_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F222959_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3e98a2b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n=撚吊資料=<br />\n中文名: 黃嘉灝 <br />\n英文名: Wong Ka Ho<br />\n舊電話: 6193 1991<br />\n生日:&nbsp; 1992-04-11 或者 1993-04-11<br />\n住址: 以前住屯門良景，2014年8月左右搬左，應該仲係良景或者去左良景<br />\n<br />\nFB: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ho.ka.399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fho.ka.399&d=12Zo%2FuCTu563fDPCZyjaHTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=e1d444c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ho.ka.399</a><br />\nIG: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/kaho411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fkaho411&d=12Zo%2FuCTu563fDPCZyjaHTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=abed575a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/kaho411</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/015109_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F015109_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=08e98e7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n=事情經過=<br />\n我個FD四年前岩岩畢業，去左間西餅鋪做pt，後尾同左個同事拍拖。點知條友原來係撚吊黎, 玩弄我個fd感情&amp;利用同情心。佢成日話自己屋企人發生意外，令佢錢銀上好手緊；又用各種藉口，多次問我個fd借錢。實質佢就係呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個仆街一直扮死狗，個fd又衰心軟，前前後後借左六皮幾比佢。(散左之後借)，我個fd就用wts追數(大約一個月一次)。但條撚吊一直拖佢，前前後後淨係還左幾千，幾個月前，條撚頭仲轉埋電話號碼，而家完全聯絡唔到佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n=對話記錄=<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225353_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225353_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=16d6b9e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有冇巴打識佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225405_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225405_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4d728bd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225414_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225414_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=045c9f98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225728_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225728_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ce97ddec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225420_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225420_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2adb5aed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225426_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225426_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=373933e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225435_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225435_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=754900a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225441_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225441_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b2bbdcaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發住燒都不忘呃錢，真係敬業樂業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225448_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225448_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=77d4d007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225455_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225455_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=053e1642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225514_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225514_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=434f6963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225521_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225521_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=85df3cb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n借老母過橋,正狗撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225532_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225532_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c7af0ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到底有幾部電話，賣唔撚完咁既?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225543_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225543_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=fef60d52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過左成個月都死唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225707_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225707_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8f18b7d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225553_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225553_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5fcf89bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又借老母過橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225603_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225603_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=deb70f24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225611_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225611_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=74d0acc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225616_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225616_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8125556d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真傻定假傻，借左人幾多錢都唔知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225621_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225621_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4ceb27ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/225637_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F225637_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f030ca51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前扮鵪鶉，而家惡過狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n=入數紙=<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/230001_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F230001_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bdeee9da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/230010_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F230010_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f4c0fd95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/234627_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F234627_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=db2c070e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吊你老母，有錢去旅行，冇錢還人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe42cf94cd7529806cc42554fa57e46710ae058","tid":607664,"uid":77092,"